data.description: Peaceful country living!  Seller says lots of wildlife walk across the yard often.  This great 3 bed, 2 bath house is zoned for Medina School District with school bus stops at the house.  Sitting on an acre with an oversized garage, you have lots of room to spread out.    Inside you will find an updated kitchen, new laminate hardwood flooring throughout, new ceramic tile flooring in the bathrooms,  primary bathroom remodel, fresh paint, and new fixtures.  Seller had a new well tank installed in 2022.
